      <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
      <p>
        I will not sell, rent, or share your personal information (email, IP address, etc.) with a
        third party, unless required by law. I collect anonymous information that you provide through
        the use of <a href="https://www.google.com/analytics" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Analytics</a>
        (which uses cookies) while you browse the site.
      </p>
      <p>
        Any email addresses are used to respond to comments on Katie Crafts. IP addresses may be used to
        block or blacklist users who are violating the Terms &amp; Conditions. When commenting, the name you
        enter is displayed along with the comment and your avatar (if set).
      </p>

      <hr>

